com.siperian.sif.message.mrm

Class SearchResponseBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.siperian.sif.message.SiperianResponse
      • com.siperian.sif.message.mrm.SearchResponseBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataProvider, RecordsProvider, Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GetAssignedRecordsResponse, GetMatchedRecordsResponse, SearchHmQueryResponse, SearchLookupValuesResponse, SearchMatchResponse, SearchQueryResponse

    public abstract class SearchResponseBase
extends SiperianResponse
implements RecordsProvider, DataProvider
    Base class for search responses.

    Each response contains a list of records, a search token to use to fetch more results, and an optional count of matching records.

    See Also:
    GetSearchResultsRequest, Serialized Form
